<div><head>《周景式孝子傳》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.2">周景式孝子傳<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.3">《管寧》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.4">管寧避地遼東，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.5">遇風，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.6">船人危懼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.7">皆叩頭悔過。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.8">寧自惟無諐咎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.9">念常如廁不冠而已。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.10">向天叩頭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.11">風亦尋靜。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-1a.12">《御覽》六十、一百八十六、《藝文類聚》八、《事類賦注》六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.2">《荊樹連陰》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.3">古有兄弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.4">忽欲分異，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.5">出門見三荊樹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.6">株接葉連，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.7">陰歎曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.8">「本猶欲聚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.9">況我兄弟而欲殊哉！」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.10">遂還，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.11">相為雍和也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.12">一曰田真兄弟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-2a.13">《御覽》四百十六、九百五十九、《藝文類聚》八十九、《初學記》十七引並仝。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.2">《猴母負子》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.3">余嘗至綏安縣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.4">途逢逐猴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.5">猴母負子沒水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.6">水雖深而清，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.7">乃以戟刺之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.8">自脅以下中斷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.9">脊尚連，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.10">抄著船中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.11">子隋其傍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.12">以手捫子而死。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1330_CHANT_001-3a.13">《御覽》九百十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
